{"tid":88034,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"啲蝗同廢老一樣都係咁鍾意詐傻扮懵","createTime":"2017-01-20T09:48:28.000Z","updateTime":"2017-01-20T10:52:53.000Z","uid":319,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"6d5c472c11fe566fafb51c66d2fecb57afd12ec1","tid":88034,"uid":319,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-20T09:48:28.000Z","msg":"屌佢老母<br />\n啱啱去7-11增値<br />\n排緊隊個陣無啦啦有個濃烈鄉音嘅蝗入嚟問個收銀有無紙巾<br />\n然後收銀就答佢喺下面個櫃<br />\n跟住隻蝗就拎左兩包紙巾就咁放入個手袋到<br />\n收銀見到就叫佢：「喂 要比錢㗎 一包四個半！」<br />\n跟住隻蝗就拎四個半出嚟放喺個櫃面到<br />\n然後個收銀就再話：「要排隊㗎，同埋兩包係九蚊！」<br />\n<br />\n屌佢老母死蝗蟲成日想詐傻扮懵<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9b1a3666ac4b56880c474c278c0388b8e509970e","tid":88034,"uid":39796,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-20T09:52:05.000Z","msg":"慘得過香港人乜事都企廢老個邊<br />\n痴9線"},{"pid":"5916a31b4917a7f9dbaf9c090d261fa8116f5625","tid":88034,"uid":56957,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-20T09:53:13.000Z","msg":"到底啲蝗個腦入面係點思考<br />\n有無人有能力分析下<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5db49813d7bbe61e554259011261386b35a13d07","tid":88034,"uid":319,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-20T09:56:17.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>慘得過香港人乜事都企廢老個邊<br />\n痴9線</blockquote><br />\n廢老同蝗一樣理應去處死<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"aab3e0c499e227550dc300859fe055774036920c","tid":88034,"uid":46609,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-20T10:00:03.000Z","msg":"咁你個刻唔屌鳩佢？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n你一出聲一定大把人跟住屌"},{"pid":"1eafd88b43f37eaae55fb01662bb170a6f41db43","tid":88034,"uid":319,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-20T10:01:45.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>咁你個刻唔屌鳩佢？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n你一出聲一定大把人跟住屌</blockquote><br />\n準備屌個下個收銀開左聲"},{"pid":"2f0956ba837f9b8c31c145cecfe630ccf4a988c